4.74</td></tr><tr><td>紫金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02899:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02899\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02899-HK</a>)</td><td>20.20</td><td>+5.98</td></tr><tr><td>萬國數據(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09698:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09698\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09698-HK</a>)</td><td>26.45</td><td>無升跌</td></tr><tr><td>網易雲音樂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09899:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09899\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09899-HK</a>)</td><td>249.00</td><td>+6.50</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
