s_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06908\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06908-HK</a>)</td><td>0.51元</td><td>跌3.77%</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　(hc)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
