            "title": "醫揚榮獲「2025年第九屆經濟部國家產業創新獎」以創新科技驅動智慧醫療發展",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6017911%2Fxl%2F9984e1bf8a349a125df18361fa7b3641.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">醫揚榮獲「2025年第九屆經濟部國家產業創新獎」，以創新科技驅動智慧醫療發展。(圖：醫揚提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>醫揚科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6569:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6569\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6569-TW</a>) 榮獲經濟部頒發「2025 年第九屆國家產業創新獎－卓越創新中小企業獎」殊榮。此項殊榮肯定了醫揚在智慧醫療技術、人工智慧應用及系統整合創新領域的卓越貢獻與持續投入，並彰顯公司以「Bring medical AI innovation with care」為使命，致力推動台灣智慧醫療產業於國際市場的領導地位。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><h6>深耕醫療運算核心技術 建構 AI 驅動醫療解決方案 </h6></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>醫揚自 2010 年成立以來，專精於醫療級運算設備與行動照護系統之研發製造，並持續深化人工智慧與資通訊技術整合能力。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此次獲獎的核心技術產品「高效能 AI 醫療影像運算平台」，採用 Intel(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>) 處理器架構搭配 NVIDIA(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 高效能 GPU，已成功導入手術導航系統、醫學影像智慧分析及即時病患監護等臨床應用場域，有效提升醫療從業人員診斷效率與臨床決策精確度。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><h6>構建智慧醫療生態體系 實踐永續發展策略 </h6></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>醫揚秉持以使用者為中心的設計理念，深入了解臨床醫療實務需求，在產品開發過程中整合靜音散熱技術、抗菌材料應用、長效電池續航及遠端設備管理等關鍵功能，全面回應醫療現場之實際應用挑戰。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>同時，積極推展 AI 輔助診療與遠距醫療照護解決方案，協助醫療機構優化營運效率、擴大偏遠地區醫療服務覆蓋率，並於硬體設計中導入節能環保技術架構，落實企業環境、社會及治理 (ESG) 永續經營承諾。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><h6>以創新為基石 擘劃智慧醫療未來願景 </h6></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮獲國家產業創新獎，不僅是對醫揚團隊專業能力與創新成果的權威認可，更代表公司未來發展的重要里程碑。醫揚將以此為契機，持續強化與國際醫療機構、頂尖 AI 科技企業合作關係，推動智慧醫療技術在臨床實務中的深度應用與普及，致力成為全球醫療產業數位轉型的關鍵技術供應商。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>總經理莊富鈞表示，此次獲獎不僅是對團隊長期努力的肯定，更是對所有致力於醫療服務第一線工作者的致敬。我們將持續以創新技術為驅動力，讓智慧醫療更加普及，讓生命照護更加安全可靠。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
